  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "アダムス・ファミリーは、映画のキャラクターや設定に基づいたプラットフォームゲームです（この映画は、1960年代の有名なテレビシリーズに基づいており、そのテレビシリーズはチャールズ・アダムスの同名の漫画に基づいています。この漫画は1930年代に『ニューヨーカー』誌に掲載されていました）。\n\nゲームは映画の終盤に設定されています。アダムス・ファミリーは、裏切り者の弁護士タリー・アルフォードによって発行された裁判所の命令により、自宅から追い出されてしまいました。さらに悪いことに、他のアダムス家のメンバー、モーティシア、パグズリー、ウェンズデー、グランニー、そしてラーチが行方不明になっています。\n\nあなたはゴメスとなり、失った家族を探してアダムス邸を巡り、神秘的なモンスターと戦い、罠を避けながら、最終的には宿敵タリーに立ち向かうことになります。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Creepy, Kooky, Ooky, Spooky! Morticia has been kidnapped!\n\nUncle Fester has lost his memory and has fallen under the spell of Abigail Craven, a conniving character who is anxious to lay her greedy hands on the Addams' hidden fortune. Having recruited a misled Uncle Faster, and assisted by her cohorts, Tully and The Judge, she managers to capture and imprison the other members of the Addams Family within the huge Addams Mansion! Only Gomez can save the day by freeing his son Pugsley, his daughter Wednesday, and Granny- and by restoring Uncle Fester's memory. Accomplishing these tasks is daunting enough, but then Gomez must seek out Morticia in the underground vaults of the Addams Mansion and confront the evil Judge in a kooky and spooky climax!",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "The Addams Family's lawyer, Tully Alford, has taken control of their Gothic mansion and imprisoned Morticia Addams, Pugsley Addams, Wednesday Addams, Granny and Uncle Fester. The player controls Gomez Addams as he explores the various rooms in the mansion, locating items and battling monsters, until he has located all of the lost family members. The game has an almost completely open-world format, unusual for games of this era, which gives players the freedom to choose what order they will save the family members in. However, Gomez cannot save Morticia until the rest of the family is rescued.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
